resources.string: Yenza isipele idatha ku-akhawunti yakho ye-Google.
Yenza isipele idatha yakho ku-akhawunti ye-Google. Buyisela ukwenziwa kwesipele kwangaphambilini kule divayisi.
Idatha ifaka izinhlelo zokusebenza, izilungiselelo zohlelo lokusebenza, izilungiselelo zesistimu, namaphasiwedi we-Wi-Fi.
Vumela izinhlelo zokusebenza zinqume kangcono indawo yakho. Idatha yendawo engaziwa izoqoqwa iphinde ithunyelwe ku-Google.
Ukuze uthole ukunemba okuthuthukisiwe nezinye izinjongo, skena amanethiwekhi we-Wi‑Fi, ngisho noma i-Wi‑Fi ivaliwe.

Isevisi yendawo ye-Google isebenzisa i-Wi-Fi namanye amasiginali ukuze inqume indawo ngokuqondile kakhulu nangokushesha, ngokuvamisile ngokusetshenziswa kwamandla okuphansi kune-GPS. Enye idatha ingalondolozwa kudivayisi yakho. Idatha ingaqoqwa noma ngabe kungekho izinhlelo zokusebenza ezisebenzayo.
Ngazise ngezindaba kanye nalokho okunikezwa kusuka ku-Google Play.

Ungashintsha lezi zinketho noma kunini kuzilungiselelo.

Ukusebenzisa kwakho le foni kungaphansi kwezinqubomgomo zobumfihlo neminye imigom yokusetshenziswa. "Funda kabanzi
Ifoni yakho ilungiselelwe ukusebenza futhi ikulungele ukusetshenziswa.
Qala i-Verizon Backup Assistant ukubuyisa oxhumana nabo kusuka kolunye ucingo le-Verizon.
Ukuze ufake ikhadi lakho le-SIM, funda imiyalelo eze nefoni yakho.
Ifoni idinga ukuthi ilande iphinde ifake isibuyekezo sesofthiwe kusukela ku-Google.
Ngokuqhubeka uphinde uthole lesi sibuyekezo sesofthiwe, uvumela Imigomo Yesevisi ye-Google kanye nokuthi Inqubomgomo Yemfihlo.
Ngokungena ngemvume, uyavumelana nemigomo yesevisi, inqubomgomo yemfihlo, imigomo yesevisi ye-Google Play yakwa-Google.
Idivayisi yakho ye-Android ayixhunyiwe kunethiwekhi ye-Wi-Fi. Ukuze ubuke lolu lwazi manje, vakashela i-%s ngesiphequluli sewebhu.
Qhubeka ngokucindezela isikrini uze uzwe umsindo ukuze unike amandla imodi yokufinelela.
Vumela i-Google ukuba ihlole zonke izinhlelo zokusebenza ezifakiwe ukuze ithole ukuziphatha okungase kube yingozi okungase kuthinte ukuphepha kwedivayisi noma idatha yakho.
Sebenzisa i-akhawunti yakho ye-Google ukwenza isipele izinhlelo zokusebenza, izilungiselelo (njengokubheka uphawu lokubekisa namaphasiwedi e-Wi-Fi), nenye idatha.
Letha izinhlelo zokusebenza, izilungiselelo, nenye idatha kule foni oyenze isipele ngaphambilini kwi-akhawunti yakho ye-Google.
Vumela i-Google ukuba isebenzise ulwazi lwakho ukwenza ngendlela ethandwa nguwe okuqukethwe nezikhangiso okukumawebhusayithi angewona awe-Google.
Ngazise ngezindaba kanye nalokho okunikezwa ku-Google Play.
Thumela ngokuzenzakalela ulwazi lomcimbi wedivayisi nelokuthola inkinga ku-Google ukusiza ukuthuthukisa imikhiqizo yethu futhi uvikele idivayisi yakho.
